  "hint": "This isn't a standard binary counter — it wraps at 3 instead of 4! Design custom next-state logic: D₀ = Q₁ NOR Q₀ (only set when 00), D₁ = NOT(Q₁) AND Q₀ (only set when 01). Need 2 D-FFs + combinational next-state logic.",
